item.dc:creator: @asshole_rule asshole_rule
item.description:
@asshole_rule wrote:

[quote=“davedavy, post:6, topic:427770”]First , thanks for this amazing fast reply’s!

There isn’t any linked path into the bat file:

@echo off title GazaaScape by Arab, 'Arab, `Omaration, Dezm cd src cd .. java -Xms250m -Xmx1024m -classpath bin;deps/* com.rs2hd.Main pause

And i’m using GazaaScape , if that one is a bade one, wich other one is a good one then?[/quote]

Replace your run.bat with this

@echo off title GazaaScape by Arab, 'Arab, `Omaration, Dezm cd src cd .. "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_25\bin\java.exe" -Xms250m -Xmx1024m -classpath bin;deps/* com.rs2hd.Main pause
